// LOCATION CONTROLLER
GET METHOD:
-----------
http://localhost:9090/LocationController/viewAllLocation
---------------------------------------------------------
OUTPUT:
-------
{
    {
        "LocationId": "1",
        "LocationName": "Chennai",
        "Locationcode": "440010",
	       "country": "INDIA",
	      " airportName":"Chennai International Airport",
    }
}
-----------------------------------------------------------
